File:Vincent Willem van Gogh 128.jpg|alt=A ceramic vase with sunflowers on a yellow surface against a pale blue background.|''[[Sunflowers (painting)|Still Life: Vase with Twelve Sunflowers]]'', August 1888. [[Neue Pinakothek]], Munich
File:Irises-Vincent van Gogh.jpg|alt=Irises growing in a garden. There is bare soil visible and orange flowers in the background.|''[[Irises (painting)|Irises]]'', 1889. [[J. Paul Getty Museum]], Los Angeles
File:Vincent van Gogh - Almond blossom - Google Art Project.jpg|alt=Pale pink blossoms on the branches of a tree against a pale blue sky.|''[[Almond Blossoms|Almond Blossom]]'', 1890. Van Gogh Museum, Amsterdam
